Package project1

Class Member

java.lang.Object
project1.Member
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Member>
public class Member extends Object implements Comparable<Member>
Member class is the class that contains the information of one member. Contains name, dob, expiration date, and location.
Author:
Ryan S. Lee, Elliott Ng

      public int compareTo(Member member)

      Specified by:

      Parameters:
      member - the member to be compared.
      Returns:
      -1 if this member is earlier, 1 if this member is later, 0 if both are same.
